{"tid":2140452,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港共党安狗應該學當年64 整一份<<通緝令>>公告天下, 夠膽通緝唔夠膽出公文?","createTime":"2020-08-05T04:19:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T04:20:40.000Z","uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8be9a8802f2dd765331e591525027bf58cb4abd6","tid":2140452,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T04:19:25.000Z","msg":"1989年6月13日，中華人民共和國公安部向全國轉發北京市公安局通緝令，搜捕六四事件北京市高校學生自治聯合會在逃分子21人。<br />\n<br />\n非法組織「北京市高校學生自治聯合會」（「高自聯」）在北京煽動，組織反革命暴亂，現決定對其在逃的頭頭和骨幹份子王丹等二十一人實施通緝（通緝名單及體貌特徵、照片附後），請接此通緝令後，立即部署查緝，發現後及予拘留，並即告北京市公安局。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikisource.org/zh-hant/%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%B8%82%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E5%B1%80%E6%90%9C%E6%8D%95%E2%80%9C%E9%AB%98%E8%87%AA%E8%81%94%E2%80%9D%E5%9C%A8%E9%80%83%E5%88%86%E5%AD%90%E9%80%9A%E7%BC%89%E4%BB%A4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikisource.org%2Fzh-hant%2F%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%25B1%2580%25E6%2590%259C%25E6%258D%2595%25E2%2580%259C%25E9%25AB%2598%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%2581%2594%25E2%2580%259D%25E5%259C%25A8%25E9%2580%2583%25E5%2588%2586%25E5%25AD%2590%25E9%2580%259A%25E7%25BC%2589%25E4%25BB%25A4&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7ZeakcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=a6c04b7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikisource.org/zh-hant/%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%B8%82%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E5%B1%80%E6%90%9C%E6%8D%95%E2%80%9C%E9%AB%98%E8%87%AA%E8%81%94%E2%80%9D%E5%9C%A8%E9%80%83%E5%88%86%E5%AD%90%E9%80%9A%E7%BC%89%E4%BB%A4</a>"},{"pid":"619ec90c5d0857a1e23df5f5dd0cee7cf25b51bc","tid":2140452,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T04:20:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yKKNfgw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyKKNfgw.jpg&h=cc62f711&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}